# Frontend

## Components
- mettascope - visualization/replay (TypeScript)
- observatory - training dashboard (React)
- gridworks - web interface (Next.js)

## Development
- Use `pnpm run dev` in each directory
- Strict TypeScript, interfaces over types
- Functional components with hooks
- Support file:// and wandb:// policy URIs